videos.description: After a Duke basket, Armando Bacot gets behind the defense for the wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: Bacot gets the transition jam

videos.description: Joey Baker finds the cutting Vernon Carey Jr. for the layup plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey gets the and-1 to go) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Carey gets the and-1 to go

videos.description: Christian Keeling knocks down mid-range jumpers on three straight possessions extending the Tar Heels' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Keeling scores 6 straight on mid-range jumpers) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Keeling scores 6 straight on mid-range jumpers

videos.description: Cassius Stanley shows off the athleticism by hanging in the air and getting the tough layup to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley gets the tough layup to fall) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Stanley gets the tough layup to fall

videos.description: Leaky Black finds Armando Bacot for the slam getting the Tar Heel crowd hyped.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot's dunk gets the crowd on their feet) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Bacot's dunk gets the crowd on their feet

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. drives through the lane and gets the tough fadeaway to go while being fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey gets the fadeaway to fall plus the foul) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Carey gets the fadeaway to fall plus the foul

videos.description: Cole Anthony drives down the lane and avoids the charge call plus getting the bucket to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Anthony avoids the charge and gets the and-1 to go) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Anthony avoids the charge and gets the and-1 to go

videos.description: Tre Jones knocks the ball loose from Cole Anthony, then gets down the court for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones strips Anthony and gets the layup) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Jones strips Anthony and gets the layup

videos.description: Leaky Black throws the lob to Garrison Brooks for the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Black finds Brooks for the dunk) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Black finds Brooks for the dunk

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. fouls out with a little over four minutes remaining, as he's walking off the court he shakes hands with UNC head coach Roy Williams.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke's Vernon Carey Jr. shakes Roy Williams' hand after fouling out) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Duke's Vernon Carey Jr. shakes Roy Williams' hand after fouling out

videos.description: After a Cole Anthony turnover, Garrison Brooks blocks Cassius Stanley's layup with under ten seconds remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Duke forces a Cole Anthony turnover late but can't convert) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Duke forces a Cole Anthony turnover late but can't convert

videos.description: Tre Jones intentionally misses the free throw, grabs his own rebound and then knocks down the jumper at the buzzer to force overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jones intentionally misses free throw, then ties the game with a jumper) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Jones intentionally misses free throw, then ties the game with a jumper

videos.description: After a missed free throw, Tre Jones puts up the shot and it comes up short but Wendell Moore Jr. puts it in giving Duke the 98-96 win over UNC in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wendell Moore Jr. plays hero for Duke in OT after Tre Jones miss) 2020/02/08

videos.headline: Wendell Moore Jr. plays hero for Duke in OT after Tre Jones miss

videos.description: Duke battles back in both regulation and overtime, capped off by a Wendell Moore Jr. buzzer-beater to top North Carolina 98-96.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Duke pulls off two miracles in OT win over UNC) 2020/02/08 SOTFULL

videos.headline: Duke pulls off two miracles in OT win over UNC
